summary.description:
Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 4.2°C) and outside temperature (up 3.2°C) and more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 9%) and rainfall (up 0.6 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in pressure (up 10 mbar), cloud levels (up 625 m), and light levels (up 4139 lux).

The past week and month had observable variation in light levels (up 7845 lux) and cloud levels (up 1028 m) when compared to today.
